applicaiton installation 

1. creates binary files /bin /sbin  /usr/sbin

2. library files which required for binary files to execute  will be in /lib  /usr/lib 

3. applicaiton settings/configuration files under /etc 

4.  logs will be genetated under  /var

    
     OS logs 
    /var/log/messages  -- redhat and centOS
    /var/log/syslog    -- ubuntu based 
    /var/adm/messages   -- Solaris 
    /var/log/syslog     -- IBM AIX 
    


